description: This file sets up the entry point for a React application, rendering the main App component inside a DOM element with id 'root'. It includes import statements for React, ReactDOM, styles, and the main App component, and initiates rendering within a React.StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM at the specified root element.
